    "description": "We at Birla Tyres Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Process Engineer based out of Visakhapatnam. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Birla Tyres Holdings Services:\nBirla Tyres Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Birla Tyres Holdings Services!",
